HEADWORD: Tragedian
<hw>Tra*ge"di*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>trag⟦eacute⟧dien</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A writer of tragedy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thence what the lofty, grave, <qex>tragedians</qex> taught.</q>
